Text.Value: You think of Shar - could she be speaking to you here at last, in the dark...?
This feels familiar. Search your memories...
*Your mind is a canyon, and the words echo from every crevasse.*
Probe your memories. What magic might this be?
((*who is it. what do they want. are we safe*))
Pray for fortitude against this mental trespass.
*Telepathic mushroom creatures - myconids - inhabit the Underdark. You must be nearing a myconid colony.*

EditorData.AnimationTags: *DUPE*[Player] End Unique animation of Player telepathy

Text.Value: Fill your mind with the words of your oath. Drown out the voice.
*You cannot identify the voice's origins.*

EditorData.AnimationTags: *DUPE*[Player] End Unique animation of Player telepathy

Text.Value: I don't know who you are, but you're not welcome in my head.
That voice... it doesn't sound like me. My mind doesn't bother giving warnings...
((*they're coming. you're coming*))

EditorData.AnimationTags: *DUPE*[Player] End Unique animation of Player telepathy

Text.Value: Panic: is the Butler back? You almost feel his beady eye upon your back.
Continue forward.

EditorData.AnimationTags: *DUPE*[Player] End Unique animation of Player telepathy

Text.Value: Who are you? What are you?
Who's coming? Cazador's minions? Have they found me?
Still your thoughts to this new voice intruding on you.
((*more are coming*))
Consider the voice. What sort of creature speaks this way?
((*closer. they're coming closer*))

EditorData.AnimationTags: [Player] End Unique animation of Player telepathy

Text.Value: ((*they're coming. they're coming*))

EditorData.AnimationTags: [Player] Unique aniomation of Player telepathy Loop

Text.Value: Ignore your tightening chest. Surely the devils hadn't found you down here?
Still your mind. You have heard many voices - but never this one.
Ignore the voice.

Synopsis:
Non has met: Triggers if the player is alone when first hearing the myconid circle's collective voice.

Hasmet: Occurs second time, regardless of how mnay players are in party. Player hears a strange voice, and has a reaction to it. Second time: Tries to respond to it.
